data.description: Located 15 miles from town this lodge-like home on a beautiful 2-acre property is in the perfect location for privacy and quiet. Walk through the custom-made, Knotty Alder door into the spacious 2,480 sq ft home that boasts a cozy and rustic atmosphere, with natural wood finishes and stone accents throughout. The kitchen, living areas, bedrooms, and bathrooms all feature vaulted ceilings with incredible woodwork that offers an out-of-town, cabin feel. Even better is the expansive deck that overlooks the private backyard with access to two creeks, plenty of garden space featuring beautiful Perennials, and a huge 3-bay shop perfect for vehicles and storage. Your new peaceful retreat awaits, welcome home!
